Description: Open-source virtual secondary displays for Linux
 Orbiscreen creates a real virtual display via DisplayLink's evdi kernel
 module and streams it over WebRTC to Android tablets and phones over Wi-Fi
 or USB (adb reverse). The native Wayland path uses the xdg-desktop-portal
 ScreenCast interface; the X11 path uses x11rb GetImage.
 .
 This package does NOT install the evdi kernel module. See the README for
 module install instructions; Secure Boot systems will need a signed DKMS
 module.